title: Jason Derulo - Don't Wanna Go Home (Official Video)
description: Jason Derulo's new Album 'Talk Dirty' is now available In Stores & on iTunes! http://smarturl.it/TalkDirtyAlbum The album features the smash hit singles "Trumpets", "Wiggle", "Talk Dirty", "The Other Side", and "Marry Me"; and also appearances from Snoop Dogg, 2 Chainz, Kid Ink, Tyga, and Jordin Sparks Producers on the album include: Timbaland, Dr. Luke, DJ Mustard, Red One and Wallpaper.
